summary: An ordinance accepting deeds and easements from Kenneth J. Morford and others to portions of the NE 1/4 of the SE 1/4 of the NW 1/4 of Section 31, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and other properties, for street and slope purposes and laying off North 100th Street, North 98th Street, Corliss Ave. North, Greenwood Ave. North, North 143rd Street, 5th Ave. Northeast, Seward Park Ave. South, and a public alley.
